Child Population: Zip Code level data from Census Bureau products represent data by Zip Coda Tabulation Area (ZCTA). ZCTAs are Census statistical areas that are designed to approximate USPS ZIP codes, through the aggregation of census blocks where a majority of addresses have the same zip code. For more information on ZCTAs, see this U.S. Census Bureau link.
